        "text": "Then the high priest rent his clothes.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—It is noticeable that St. Mark uses the word for the inner garment, St. Matthew that for the outer.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
